@DATABASE "GunFright"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - G - GunFright"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - G
                   ====================================

                                 GunFright
                                 =========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49233,0)"}         49233,0
@{"Infinite Ammo " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(51711,0)"}         51711,0
@{"Infinite Ammo+" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(51711,201)"}         51711,201
@{"No Enemies    " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(46022,0) ZXAMPoke(48224,0)"}         46022,0:48224,0
@{"Infinite Money" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(54122,201)"}         54122,201
@{"Stop Quickdraw" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(47919,0) ZXAMPoke(47920,0)"}         47919,0:47920,0



                         This is one of my POKEs (except for the "No
                         Enemies" and "Stop Quickdraw" POKES). Enjoy!

                         I don't know if the "Stop Enemies" actually
                         works or not. It didn't stop the women who
                         can kill you from appearing. 

                         I think the "Stop Quickdraw" works, but I could
                         never find the wanted criminal, and I played it 
                         for over an hour! ZZZzzz.... All I can think of
                         is that possibly the POKE removes the wanted
                         person completely! Maybe, maybe not.

                         Rastan.
@endnode
